Package rsb.methods

Class Skills

java.lang.Object
rsb.methods.MethodProvider
rsb.methods.Skills
public class Skills extends MethodProvider
This class is for all the skill calculations. Example usage: skills.getRealLevel(Skills.ATTACK);
